Description: The flight into Egypt; fourth state Engraving
Producer name: Print made by: Israhel van Meckenem
After: Master of the Martyrdom of the Ten Thousand
Curator's comments: Suite of 55 sheets and 4 variations, in large parts copied after the Master of the Martyrdom of the 10,000 (L 8-53, and based on an original series by the Master of the Berlin Passion, cf. L III, pp. 383-6).
Bibliographic references: Lehrs 1908-34 / Geschichte und kritische Katalog des deutschen, niederländischen und französischen Kupferstichs im XV Jahrhundert (IX.87.74.IV)
